ZH: 1. 艰苦奋斗是取得成功的必经之路。
EN: 1. Hard struggle is the path to success.

ZH: 2. 在这个疫情期间，医护人员们正在艰苦奋斗。
EN: 2. During this pandemic, medical workers are struggling hard.

ZH: 3. 学生们必须艰苦奋斗才能取得好成绩。
EN: 3. Students must work hard to achieve good grades.

ZH: 4. 不怕艰苦奋斗，只怕心态崩溃。
EN: 4. Not afraid of hard struggle, only fear mental breakdown.

ZH: 5. 他们愿意在贫困的环境下艰苦奋斗，为了给子女提供更好的生活。
EN: 5. They are willing to struggle hard in poverty, in order to provide a better life for their children.

ZH: 6. 那个小镇的居民们正在艰苦奋斗，重建家园。
EN: 6. The residents of that town are struggling hard to rebuild their homes.

ZH: 7. 青年一代应该懂得艰苦奋斗，才能拥有更美好的未来。
EN: 7. The younger generation should understand hard struggle in order to have a better future.

ZH: 8. 伟大的领袖曾说过：我们要艰苦奋斗，战胜一切困难。
EN: 8. The great leader once said: We must struggle hard and overcome all difficulties.

ZH: 9. 艰苦奋斗可以磨练一个人的意志。
EN: 9. Hard struggle can temper a person's will.

ZH: 10. 乡村教师们一直在默默地艰苦奋斗，为孩子们提供更好的教育。
EN: 10. Rural teachers have been silently struggling hard to provide children with better education.

ZH: 11. 为了实现自己的梦想，他必须经历艰苦奋斗。
EN: 11. In order to achieve his dream, he must go through hard struggle.

ZH: 12. 要想在竞争激烈的职场中脱颖而出，必须艰苦奋斗。
EN: 12. In order to stand out in the fiercely competitive workplace, one must struggle hard.

ZH: 13. 我们要始终坚定信念，勇敢面对挑战，艰苦奋斗。
EN: 13. We must always have firm faith, bravely face challenges, and struggle hard.

ZH: 14. 他们在农村劳作，艰苦奋斗，过着简朴而充实的生活。
EN: 14. They work in rural areas, struggle hard, and lead a simple but fulfilling life.

ZH: 15. 雨季来临，农民们要艰苦奋斗，田里的庄稼才能生长茂盛。
EN: 15. When the rainy season comes, farmers must struggle hard so that the crops in the fields can grow well.

ZH: 16. 这支队伍在比赛中艰苦奋斗，最终取得了胜利。
EN: 16. This team struggled hard in the game and ultimately achieved victory.

ZH: 17. 同学们要团结一致，艰苦奋斗，为班集体荣誉而努力。
EN: 17. Students must unite, struggle hard, and work hard for the honor of the class as a collective.

ZH: 18. 作为一名新手，他要经历许多艰苦奋斗才能成为一名优秀的演员。
EN: 18. As a newcomer, he must go through a lot of hard struggle to become an excellent actor.

ZH: 19. 这座城市的居民们正处于艰苦奋斗的过程中，恢复生产。
EN: 19. The residents of this city are in the process of hard struggle to resume production.

ZH: 20. 只有经历过艰苦奋斗，才能真正体会到成功的甜蜜。
EN: 20. Only through hard struggle can one truly appreciate the sweetness of success.
